                <h3>
                    Learn to convert meter into CM with an example

                </h3>
                <p>
                    Let’s say you have 50 meters of land, and you want to convert that piece of land/plot into CM, for that you just need to multiply 50 meters by 100.

                    <br>

                    CM = (50) x 100 = 5,000


                    <br>
                    Therefore, 50 meters of land/plot would be approximately equal to 5,000 CM.

